%% ODH Dashboard - Data Flow Sequence Diagram
%% Generated by: Claude Opus 4.6

sequenceDiagram
    participant Browser as User Browser
    participant Gateway as data-science-gateway<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant KRBAC as kube-rbac-proxy<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS TLS
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API Server<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant Dashboard as odh-dashboard Backend<br/>8080/TCP HTTP (localhost)
    participant Thanos as Thanos Querier<br/>9092/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant ModelRegUI as model-registry-ui<br/>8043/TCP HTTPS TLS
    participant GenAIUI as gen-ai-ui<br/>8143/TCP HTTPS TLS
    participant MaaSUI as maas-ui<br/>8243/TCP HTTPS TLS

    Note over Browser,K8sAPI: Flow 1: User Accesses Dashboard UI

    Browser->>Gateway: GET /dashboard<br/>HTTPS/443, TLS 1.2+
    Gateway->>KRBAC: Forward to rhods-dashboard:8443<br/>HTTPS, TLS (service-ca)
    KRBAC->>K8sAPI: SubjectAccessReview<br/>Can user list projects?<br/>HTTPS/443, SA token
    K8sAPI-->>KRBAC: Allowed
    KRBAC->>Dashboard: Proxy to localhost:8080<br/>HTTP, X-Auth-Request-User/Groups
    Dashboard-->>KRBAC: React SPA + Assets
    KRBAC-->>Gateway: Response
    Gateway-->>Browser: Dashboard HTML/JS

    Note over Browser,K8sAPI: Flow 2: API Call (K8s Resource Operation)

    Browser->>Gateway: GET /api/k8s/...<br/>HTTPS/443
    Gateway->>KRBAC: Forward<br/>HTTPS/8443
    KRBAC->>Dashboard: Authenticated request<br/>x-forwarded-access-token
    Dashboard->>K8sAPI: K8s API call on behalf of user<br/>HTTPS/443, Bearer token
    K8sAPI-->>Dashboard: Resource response
    Dashboard-->>KRBAC: JSON response
    KRBAC-->>Gateway: Response
    Gateway-->>Browser: JSON response

    Note over Browser,Thanos: Flow 3: Prometheus Metrics Query

    Browser->>Gateway: POST /api/prometheus/query<br/>HTTPS/443
    Gateway->>KRBAC: Forward<br/>HTTPS/8443
    KRBAC->>Dashboard: Authenticated request
    Dashboard->>Thanos: POST query<br/>HTTPS/9092, Bearer token
    Thanos-->>Dashboard: Metrics data
    Dashboard-->>Browser: Metrics response

    Note over Browser,ModelRegUI: Flow 4: Module Federation (Model Registry)

    Browser->>Gateway: GET /_mf/modelRegistry/remoteEntry.js<br/>HTTPS/443
    Gateway->>KRBAC: Forward<br/>HTTPS/8443
    KRBAC->>Dashboard: Authenticated request
    Dashboard->>ModelRegUI: Proxy to federated module<br/>HTTPS/8043, x-forwarded-access-token
    ModelRegUI-->>Dashboard: Remote entry JS
    Dashboard-->>Browser: Federated module code

    Note over Browser,K8sAPI: Flow 5: Kubernetes Watch (WebSocket)

    Browser->>Gateway: WSS /wss/k8s/...<br/>WSS/443
    Gateway->>KRBAC: WebSocket upgrade<br/>WSS/8443
    KRBAC->>Dashboard: Authenticated WebSocket
    Dashboard->>K8sAPI: Watch API<br/>WSS/443, Bearer token (base64 subprotocol)
    K8sAPI-->>Dashboard: Watch events (streaming)
    Dashboard-->>Browser: Real-time resource updates
